Package: rENM.data
Type: Package
Title: Data assembly tools for the rENM framework
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Author: John L. Schnase
Maintainer: John L. Schnase <rENM.Framework@gmail.com>
ORCID: 0000-0001-7473-3977
Description: The rENM framework is a modular sysem for 
    reconstucting and analyzing long-term ecological niche 
    dynamics using time-indexed environmental data and species 
    occurrence records. Its packages support climate-based 
    niche modeling, temporal analysis of climatic suitability, 
    and reproducible workflows for studying ecological change.
